column4: The patient presents with symptoms of Attention Deficit/Hyperactivity Disorder (ADHD), particularly the inattentive type, as indicated by difficulties with maintaining focus on tasks, easy distraction, and forgetfulness. These symptoms have significantly impaired their ability to complete projects, manage daily activities, and maintain a full-time job. Further assessment and potential referral for specialized evaluation are recommended.
